sql: SELECT Cost_per_25_miles FROM Vehicles WHERE  Combined_fuel_economy_rate >= 37
SELECT name, name, membership_credit FROM Discount WHERE  membership_credit >= 55 GROUP BY membership_credit LIMIT 8

SELECT Customers.name FROM Customers JOIN Vehicles JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id AND Vehicles.id = Renting_history.vehicles_id WHERE total_hours BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY Customers.name ASC
SELECT Combined_fuel_economy_rate, Type_of_powertrain FROM Vehicles JOIN Renting_history ON Vehicles.id = Renting_history.vehicles_id WHERE  customer_id != 92 ORDER BY Combined_fuel_economy_rate DESC

SELECT SUM(Customers.id), MAX(membership_credit), COUNT(vehicles_id) FROM Customers JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id WHERE vehicles_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  total_hours <= 96 LIMIT 2
SELECT AVG(vehicles_id), AVG(vehicles_id) FROM Customers JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id WHERE  Customers.id <= 39 LIMIT 3
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.Annual_fuel_cost), a.Model_year, a.Notes FROM Vehicles AS a WHERE  a.Model_year = 39 LIMIT 8
SELECT name FROM Customers WHERE  membership_credit <= 78

SELECT MIN(id), COUNT(total_hours), customer_id FROM Renting_history WHERE id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND discount_id != (SELECT MAX(discount_id) FROM Renting_history AS x WHERE  x.total_hours != 48) GROUP BY customer_id ORDER BY customer_id DESC
SELECT m.id FROM Discount AS m WHERE m.membership_credit BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  m.id != 86 ORDER BY m.id DESC
SELECT AVG(g.membership_credit), g.id FROM Discount JOIN Discount AS g ON Discount.id = g.id WHERE  g.membership_credit != 73
SELECT SUM(u.age), u.id, u.membership_credit FROM Customers AS u WHERE u.id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY u.membership_credit HAVING AVG(u.id) > 95 LIMIT 2
SELECT membership_credit FROM Discount JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.discount_id = Discount.id WHERE  customer_id <= 2

SELECT name, customer_id FROM Discount JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.discount_id = Discount.id WHERE membership_credit BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  total_hours >= 97 GROUP BY customer_id HAVING MAX(vehicles_id) > 50
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT j.membership_credit), j.name, j.name FROM Discount AS j WHERE  j.membership_credit >= 76 ORDER BY j.name DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT y.vehicles_id), y.total_hours, y.discount_id FROM Renting_history AS y GROUP BY y.discount_id HAVING SUM(y.total_hours) < 91 ORDER BY y.total_hours DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Notes), Customers.name FROM Customers JOIN Discount JOIN Vehicles JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.discount_id = Discount.id AND Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id AND Vehicles.id = Renting_history.vehicles_id WHERE  discount_id <= 91 ORDER BY Customers.name ASC LIMIT 8

SELECT Customers.name, Type_of_powertrain FROM Customers JOIN Discount JOIN Vehicles JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.discount_id = Discount.id AND Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id AND Vehicles.id = Renting_history.vehicles_id WHERE customer_id > (SELECT SUM(customer_id) FROM Renting_history LIMIT 6) GROUP BY Type_of_powertrain ORDER BY Type_of_powertrain ASC
SELECT t.Type_of_powertrain FROM Vehicles AS t GROUP BY t.Type_of_powertrain ORDER BY t.Type_of_powertrain DESC

SELECT Highway_fuel_economy_rate FROM Customers JOIN Discount JOIN Vehicles JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.discount_id = Discount.id AND Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id AND Vehicles.id = Renting_history.vehicles_id WHERE Annual_fuel_cost BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR City_fuel_economy_rate > (SELECT MIN(City_fuel_economy_rate) FROM Vehicles WHERE  Model_year = 78 LIMIT 5) LIMIT 2

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Discount.id), name FROM Discount JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.discount_id = Discount.id WHERE vehicles_id IN (SELECT vehicles_id FROM Renting_history WHERE id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  total_hours < 57 LIMIT 1) GROUP BY name HAVING MIN(customer_id) > 31 LIMIT 1
SELECT MIN(customer_id), vehicles_id FROM Renting_history

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Model_year), vehicles_id, Notes FROM Customers JOIN Discount JOIN Vehicles JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.discount_id = Discount.id AND Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id AND Vehicles.id = Renting_history.vehicles_id WHERE  Highway_fuel_economy_rate != 37 GROUP BY Notes HAVING MIN(Discount.membership_credit) < 50
SELECT MIN(Combined_fuel_economy_rate), Type_of_powertrain, Notes FROM Vehicles GROUP BY Notes
SELECT i.id, i.name FROM Vehicles AS i WHERE i.Combined_fuel_economy_rate BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY i.name

SELECT discount_id, total_hours FROM Customers JOIN Vehicles JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id AND Vehicles.id = Renting_history.vehicles_id WHERE  Highway_fuel_economy_rate <= 16 GROUP BY total_hours
SELECT t.name, t.name FROM Discount AS t WHERE t.membership_credit BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  t.id >= 20 GROUP BY t.name LIMIT 7

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Customers.membership_credit), Customers.name FROM Customers JOIN Discount JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.discount_id = Discount.id AND Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id WHERE  Discount.id > 37 OR discount_id IN (SELECT discount_id FROM Renting_history AS j WHERE  j.discount_id = 11) ORDER BY Customers.name DESC LIMIT 2
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT x.id), COUNT(DISTINCT x.Highway_fuel_economy_rate), x.Highway_fuel_economy_rate FROM Vehicles AS x WHERE  x.City_fuel_economy_rate < 94 ORDER BY x.Highway_fuel_economy_rate ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Notes) FROM Customers JOIN Discount JOIN Vehicles JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.discount_id = Discount.id AND Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id AND Vehicles.id = Renting_history.vehicles_id WHERE Model_year BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Renting_history WHERE  id <= 58 AND Customers.id = customer_id LIMIT 3)
SELECT vehicles_id, discount_id FROM Customers JOIN Renting_history ON Renting_history.customer_id = Customers.id ORDER BY discount_id DESC
SELECT membership_credit, name FROM Customers WHERE  membership_credit != 8
SELECT MAX(age), COUNT(membership_credit), age FROM Customers GROUP BY age
